  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>A Floating Non-platformer</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this experimental platforms, we did away with the most basic building block of the genre: The platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/54d90a53ff3e2c9c02a75f0621f25dfb.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/54d90a53ff3e2c9c02a75f0621f25dfb.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/54d90a53ff3e2c9c02a75f0621f25dfb.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Move to Groove</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a dynamic, reactive, beautifully complicated soundtrack, you'll make a new melody with every move you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/6e95affa4337a6b5389cf7d33629b3d4.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/6e95affa4337a6b5389cf7d33629b3d4.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/6e95affa4337a6b5389cf7d33629b3d4.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mesmerizing Movement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn new ways to wrap your mind around interlocking space, riding down slipstreams, dashing into reflective pads, and resting in safe, secure bubbles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/1af5ec1f6be796fd47d3157eca636a82.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/1af5ec1f6be796fd47d3157eca636a82.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/1af5ec1f6be796fd47d3157eca636a82.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doodles Come to Life</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hand-drawn art style evokes every absent-minded drawing you ever made in the margins of your school notebooks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/0f69ed61a74553b8fa8032351dfaa5ac.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/0f69ed61a74553b8fa8032351dfaa5ac.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/0f69ed61a74553b8fa8032351dfaa5ac.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fluid Difficulty</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick respawns and granular difficulty means challenge comes in all shapes and sizes-- even the shape and size of an amoeboid squid-thing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/97ddf816625c99679213258430c695f8.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/97ddf816625c99679213258430c695f8.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/97ddf816625c99679213258430c695f8.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
