"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/1af5ec1f6be796fd47d3157eca636a82.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/1af5ec1f6be796fd47d3157eca636a82.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/1af5ec1f6be796fd47d3157eca636a82.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doodles Come to Life</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hand-drawn art style evokes every absent-minded drawing you ever made in the margins of your school notebooks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/0f69ed61a74553b8fa8032351dfaa5ac.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/0f69ed61a74553b8fa8032351dfaa5ac.webm?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/0f69ed61a74553b8fa8032351dfaa5ac.mp4?t=1751348155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fluid Difficulty</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick respawns and granular difficulty means challenge comes in all shapes and sizes-- even the shape and size of an amoeboid squid-thing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015920/extras/97ddf816625c99679213258430c695f8.poster.avif?t=1751348155\" wid